headline: Oneok Q4 Earnings Top.; Stock Recently Hit Record High
summary: Natural gas producer Oneok announced revised 2025 guidance after the market closed Monday.  Oneok guided for a 2025 earnings per diluted share midpoint of $5.37, an 8% increase year over year.  Meanwhile, the Relative Strength (RS) Rating for natural gas producer Oneok rose from 70 to 73 Monday.
